# {{ shop.name }}

> {{ shop.description | default: 'FirstT designs and sells premium water shoes engineered for performance — lightweight quick-dry knit uppers, drainage soles, and grip-anywhere rubber outsoles for the beach, the boat, and the trail.' }}

FirstT is a direct-to-consumer water-shoes brand. Our shoes are designed for paddleboarders, surfers, beachgoers, kayakers, river hikers, and anyone whose feet are in and out of the water. Every pair is tested by athletes in salt, sand, sun, and reef.

## Key product details
- **Material:** Quick-dry knit polyester upper, TPR + rubber sole
- **Weight:** Approximately 180 g per shoe (US size 9)
- **Drainage:** 12+ ports per sole for instant water release
- **Grip:** Multidirectional rubber lugs rated for wet rock and pool decks
- **Sizing:** True to size, US 5–14, EU 35–48
- **Care:** Cold machine wash inside mesh bag, air dry only
- **Return policy:** 60-day try-anywhere guarantee, free returns
- **Shipping:** Free worldwide over $79 USD, 5–10 business days

## Best uses
- Paddleboarding, surfing, kayaking, sailing
- Beach walking on hot sand, rocky shores, coral reefs
- River hikes, waterfall trails, canyoneering
- Pool, gym, water aerobics
- Travel — packs flat, dries fast

## What we are not
- Not a hiking-boot replacement for cold/snow conditions
- Not insulated; not designed for wetsuit-temperature water
- Not steel-toed; not a safety / industrial shoe

